<title>USA: Goodyear sets 3-year $600 mln stock buyback.</title>
<headline>Goodyear sets 3-year $600 mln stock buyback.</headline>
<dateline>AKRON, Ohio 1997-02-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Goodyear Tire &amp; Rubber Co said its board approved a three-year $600 million stock repurchase program designed to give the company better flexibility in funding its acquisition program and to optimize shareholder value.</p>
<p>&quot;The company's strong cash flow position has convinced the Board of the timeliness of this decision,&quot; Goodyear Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Samir G. Gibara said.</p>
